eya_def_tools.data_models.assessment_process_description.AssessmentProcessDescription
Description of a process used in an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Name of the process or model use in the process. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.assessment_results.Result
Set of results for an element of an energy assessment.
Attributes: label (Optional[str]): Label of the results. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. assessment_period (AssessmentPeriod(StrEnum)): Period of or in time that has been assessed and for which the results are applicable. Default is 'lifetime'. dimensions (Optional[tuple[ResultsDimension(StrEnum), ...]]): Dimensions along which the results are binned (all result values in the same results object must have the same dimensions). Default is None. statistics (list[ResultStatistic]): List of result statistic objects that each include result values for a specific statistic type.

eya_def_tools.data_models.assessment_results.ResultStatistic
Result values for one specific statistic type.
Attributes: description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. statistic_type (StatisticType(StrEnum)): Type of statistic in the results component. values (UnionType[float, list[tuple[tuple[UnionType[float, int, str], ...], float]]]): Result as a single number or values at coordinates.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_assessment.EnergyAssessment
Energy assessment details and results.
Attributes: gross_eya_process (AssessmentProcessDescription): Specification of the model used to calculate the gross EYA estimates. gross_eya_results (list[Result]): Gross energy production predictions in GWh. plant_performance_loss_categories (list[PlantPerformanceCategory]): Plant performance loss assessment categories including results. net_energy_uncertainty_assessment (Optional[UncertaintyAssessment]): Net energy production uncertainty assessment, including the conversion of the wind resource assessment uncertainty results from wind speed to energy quantities and results for all main energy uncertainty categories. Default is None. net_eya_results (list[Result]): Net energy production predictions in GWh, including overall uncertainties and results at different confidence levels.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceCategory
Plant performance loss assessment category.
Attributes: label (PlantPerformanceCategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the plant performance loss category. subcategories (list[PlantPerformanceSubcategory]): Plant performance loss assessment subcategories that fall under the category. The subcategory objects include details and results at the subcategory level. category_results (list[Result]): Plant performance assessment category results as dimensionless loss factors (efficiencies).

eya_def_tools.data_models.uncertainty.UncertaintyAssessment
Wind resource uncertainty assessment.
Attributes: categories (list[UncertaintyCategory]): List of wind resource uncertainty assessment categories.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceSubcategory
Plant performance loss assessment subcategory.
Attributes: label (PlantPerformanceSubcategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the plant performance loss subcategory. basis (AssessmentBasis(StrEnum)): Basis of plant performance loss subcategory assessment. The basis describes the level of detail of the calculation or estimate used in the assessment of the subcategory. variability (VariabilityType(StrEnum)): Considered variability in the plant performance loss subcategory. assessment_process_descriptions (Optional[list[AssessmentProcessDescription]]): Description of calculation processes used in the assessment of the plant performance loss subcategory. Default is None. is_preliminary (bool): Whether the assessment of the plant performance loss assessment subcategory should be marked as preliminary. Default is False. elements (Optional[list[PlantPerformanceElement]]): Plant performance loss assessment elements that fall under the the subcategory. The element objects include details and results at the element level. A breakdown of plant performance loss subcategories into elements is optional and can be included only for a subset of the subcategories, as relevant. Whereas the categories and subcategories are fixed, the user may freely define element labels. Default is None. subcategory_results (Result): Plant performance assessment subcategory results as dimensionless loss factors (efficiencies).

eya_def_tools.data_models.uncertainty.UncertaintyCategory
Wind resource uncertainty assessment category.
Attributes: label (UncertaintyCategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the uncertainty category. subcategories (list[UncertaintySubcategory]): Wind resource uncertainty assessment subcategories. category_results (list[Result]): Category level assessment results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.eya_def.EyaDef
IEC 61400-15-2 EYA DEF energy yield assessment data model.
Attributes: json_uri (Optional[str]): Unique URI of the JSON document. Default is None. title (str): Title of the energy assessment report. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. project_name (str): Name of the project under assessment. document_id (Optional[str]): The ID of the report document; not including the version when 'document_version' is used. Default is None. document_version (Optional[str]): Version of the report document, also known as revision. Default is None. issue_date (date): Report issue date in the ISO 8601 standard format for a calendar date, i.e. YYYY-MM-DD. contributors (list[ReportContributor]): List of report contributors (e.g. author and verifier) issuing_organisations (list[Organisation]): The organisation(s) issuing the report (e.g. consultant). receiving_organisations (Optional[list[Organisation]]): The organisation(s) receiving the report (e.g. client), if relevant. Default is None. contract_reference (Optional[str]): Reference to contract between the issuing and receiving organisations that governs the energy yield assessment. Default is None. confidentiality_classification (Optional[str]): Confidentiality classification of the report. Default is None. coordinate_reference_system (CoordinateReferenceSystem): Coordinate reference system used for all location data. measurement_stations (list[MeasurementStationMetadata]): List of measurement station metadata JSON document(s) according to the IEA Task 43 WRA Data Model. Default is []. reference_wind_farms (Optional[list[ReferenceWindFarm]]): List of reference operational wind farms. Default is None. wind_resource_assessments (Optional[list[WindResourceAssessment]]): List of wind resource assessments, including results, at the measurement station locations. Default is None. turbine_models (Optional[list[TurbineModel]]): List of wind turbine model specifications. Default is None. scenarios (Optional[list[Scenario]]): List of energy yield assessment scenarios. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.organisation.Organisation
Issuing or receiving organisation of an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Entity name of the organisation. abbreviation (Optional[str]): Abbreviated name of the organisation. Default is None. address (Optional[str]): Address of the organisation. Default is None. contact_name (Optional[str]): Name(s) of contact person(s) in the organisation. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_wind_farm.ReferenceWindFarm
Reference wind farm metadata.
Attributes: reference_wind_farm_id (str): Unique ID for the reference wind farm within the EYA DEF document. wind_farm_configuration (WindFarmConfiguration): The configuration data for the reference wind farm. datasets (list[ReferenceWindFarmDataset]): Metadata for the operational dataset.

eya_def_tools.data_models.report_metadata.ReportContributor
Contributor to an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Name of the contributor. email_address (Optional[EmailStr]): Email address of the contributor. Default is None. contributor_type (Literal['author', 'verifier', 'approver', 'other']): Type of contributor. contribution_comments (Optional[str]): Comments to clarify contribution. Default is None. completion_date (Optional[date]): Contribution completion date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.scenario.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: scenario_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (ConstrainedFloatValue): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. wind_resource_assessment_reference (WindResourceAssessmentReference): Measurement wind resource assessment reference for the scenario. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (TurbineWindResourceAssessment): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. energy_assessment (EnergyAssessment): Energy assessment details and results, including gross energy, plant performance, net energy and uncertainties.

eya_def_tools.data_models.spatial.CoordinateReferenceSystem
Specification of a coordinate reference system for GIS data.
Attributes: system_label (str): Label of the coordinate system. epsg_srid (Optional[int]): EPSG Spatial Reference System Identifier (SRID). Default is None. wkt (Optional[str]): Well-known text (WKT) string definition of the coordinate system. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.turbine_model.TurbineModel
Specification of a wind turbine model.
Attributes: turbine_model_id (str): Unique identifier of the turbine model. label (str): Label of the turbine model. perf_spec_ref (Optional[TurbineModelSpecification]): Reference to a json document with turbine model performance specification (PLACEHOLDER). Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.WindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the measurement locations.
Attributes: measurement_station_reference (Optional[MeasurementStationReference]): Assessment results at the measurement location(s). Default is None. reference_wind_farm_reference (Optional[ReferenceWindFarmReference]): Assessment results at the measurement location(s). Default is None. subcategory_results (list[Result]): Assessment results at the measurement location(s). uncertainty_assessment (UncertaintyAssessment): Measurement wind resource uncertainty assessment.

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_wind_farm.ReferenceWindFarmDataset
Reference wind farm operational dataset metadata.
Attributes: data_supplier_organisation (Organisation): The organisation that supplied the data. data_type (OperationalDataType(StrEnum)): The type of the operational data. Primary SCADA data refers to data originating directly from the turbine OEM SCADA system. Secondary SCADA data is provided by a data management service provider who has processed the primary SCADA data and often makes it available in a harmonised format independent of OEM. Metered production refers to quantities measured by the project revenue meter. time_resolution (TimeResolution(StrEnum)): Time resolution of the data. data_period_start_date (date): Start of the data period in the ISO 8601 standard format for a calendar date, i.e. YYYY-MM-DD. data_period_end_date (date): End of the data period in the ISO 8601 standard format for a calendar date, i.e. YYYY-MM-DD.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.WindFarmConfiguration
A collection of wind turbines considered as one unit (plant).
Attributes: name (str): Name of the wind farm. label (Optional[str]): Abbreviated label of the wind farm. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. turbines (list[TurbineConfiguration]): List of specifications for constituent turbines. relevance (WindFarmRelevance(StrEnum)): The relevance of the wind farm for the assessment. operational_lifetime_start_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime start date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. operational_lifetime_end_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime end date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. wind_farm_restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the wind farm level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.TurbineWindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations.
Attributes: turbine_wind_resource_results (list[Result]): Assessment results at the turbine location(s). wind_spatial_modelling_processes (list[AssessmentProcessDescription]): Wind spatial modelling processes used in the assessment. uncertainty_assessment (Optional[UncertaintyAssessment]): Turbine wind resource uncertainty assessment. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.WindResourceAssessmentReference
Measurement wind resource assessment basis in a scenario.

eya_def_tools.data_models.measurement_station.MeasurementStationReference
Measurement station basis in a wind resource assessment.

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_wind_farm.ReferenceWindFarmReference
Reference wind farm basis in a wind resource assessment.
Attributes: reference_wind_farm_ids (list[str]): List of the IDs of all reference wind farms used in the assessment.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceElement
Plant performance loss assessment element.
Attributes: label (str): Label of the plant performance loss element. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. basis (AssessmentBasis(StrEnum)): Basis of plant performance loss element assessment. The basis describes the level of detail of the calculation or estimate used in the assessment of the element. variability (VariabilityType(StrEnum)): Considered variability in the plant performance loss element. is_independent (bool): Whether the plant performance loss element is independent of all other elements. Default is True. assessment_process_descriptions (Optional[list[AssessmentProcessDescription]]): Description of calculation processes used in the assessment of the plant performance loss element. Default is None. is_preliminary (bool): Whether the assessment of the plant performance loss assessment element should be marked as preliminary. Default is False. element_results (Result): Plant performance assessment element results as dimensionless loss factors (efficiencies).

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.OperationalRestriction
Specifications of a restriction that limits power output.
In the current draft of the schema, 'label', 'description' and 'comments' fields are available to describe the restriction with free text. This is intended to be expanded into a more comprehensive data model.
Attributes: label (str): Short label to indicate the type of operational restriction. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.TurbineConfiguration
Specification of all details for a turbine configuration.
Attributes: turbine_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the turbine specification. Default is None. label (str): Label of the turbine. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. location (Location): Horizontal location of the turbine. hub_height (float): Turbine hub height. turbine_model_id (str): Unique identifier of the turbine model. restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the turbine level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.spatial.Location
Specification of a horizontal location in space.
Attributes: location_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the location. Default is None. label (Optional[str]): Label of the location. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. x (float): Location x-coordinate (typically easing). y (float): Location y-coordinate (typically northing).
